402">Now,</span> <span begin="36.402" end="36.956">Madison</span> <span begin="36.956" end="37.140">and</span> <span begin="37.140" end="37.703">Jefferson</span> <span begin="37.703" end="37.986">are</span> <span begin="37.986" end="38.709">merciless</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">现在的麦迪逊和杰斐逊可是毫不留情</span></p><p begin="38.819" end="41.222" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="38.819" end="39.071">Well,</span> <span begin="39.471" end="39.748">hate</span> <span begin="39.748" end="39.921">the</span> <span begin="39.921" end="40.180">sin,</span> <span begin="40.180" end="40.385">love</span> <span begin="40.385" end="40.564">the</span> <span begin="40.564" end="41.222">sinner</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">咳，“恨其罪，爱其人”嘛</span></p><p begin="41.232" end="41.960" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="41.232" end="41.960">Hamilton!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">汉密尔顿！</span></p><p begin="42.165" end="43.880" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="42.165" end="42.402">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="42.402" end="42.642">sorry,</span> <span begin="42.642" end="42.867">Burr,</span> <span begin="42.867" end="43.016">I</span> <span begin="43.016" end="43.361">gotta</span> <span begin="43.361" end="43.880">go</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">抱歉，伯尔，我得走了</span></p><p begin="43.890" end="44.551" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="43.890" end="44.551">But-</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但是——</span></p><p begin="44.595" end="46.648" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="44.595" end="45.075">Decisions</span> <span begin="45.075" end="45.278">are</span> <span begin="45.278" end="45.726">happening</span> <span begin="45.726" end="46.043">over</span> <span begin="46.043" end="46.648">dinner</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">重大决定正在晚宴桌上产生</span></p><p begin="49.841" end="52.652" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="49.8