.604" end="1:03.289">financial</span> <span begin="1:03.289" end="1:03.825">power</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那个移民出来时获得了空前的财政大权</span></p><p begin="1:03.825" end="1:06.246" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:03.825" end="1:03.939">A</span> <span begin="1:03.939" end="1:04.381">system</span> <span begin="1:04.381" end="1:04.563">he</span> <span begin="1:04.563" end="1:04.747">can</span> <span begin="1:04.747" end="1:05.091">shape</span> <span begin="1:05.091" end="1:05.536">however</span> <span begin="1:05.536" end="1:05.712">he</span> <span begin="1:05.712" end="1:06.246">wants</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一个他可以随心所欲塑造的系统</span></p><p begin="1:06.522" end="1:09.615" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:06.522" end="1:06.677">The</span> <span begin="1:06.677" end="1:07.285">Virginians</span> <span begin="1:07.285" end="1:07.783">emerge</span> <span begin="1:07.783" end="1:07.991">with</span> <span begin="1:07.991" end="1:08.189">the</span> <span begin="1:08.189" end="1:08.861">nation&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:08.861" end="1:09.615">capital</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那些弗吉尼亚人出来时得到了国家的首都</span></p><p begin="1:09.782" end="1:11.557" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:09.782" end="1:09.956">And</span> <span begin="1:09.956" end="1:10.158">here&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:10.158" end="1:10.342">the</span> <span begin="1:10.342" end="1:10.693">pièce</span> <span begin="1:10.693" end="1:10.793">de</span> <span begin="1:10.793" end="1:11.557">résistance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">而这就是整件事最精妙绝伦之处（压轴戏）：</span></p><p begin="1:11.953" end="1:14.236" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:11.953" end="1:12.147">No</span> <span begin="1:12.147" end="1:12.355">one</span> <span begin="1:12.355" end="1:12.601">else</span> <span begin="1:12.601" end="1:12.742">was</span> <span begin="1:12.742" end="1:12.945">in</span> <span begin="1:12.945